exInfo.value: select MACAddress,GatewayCostMetric,Description from Win32_NetworkAdapterConfiguration where(MACAddress <> NULL)and (IPConnectionMetric > 1 )and (NOT(Description LIKE '%Virtual%'))
select ProcessorId from Win32_Processor where ProcessorId <> NULL
select SerialNumber from Win32_BIOS where SerialNumber <> NULL
select SerialNumber from Win32_DiskDrive where (SerialNumber IS NOT NULL) AND (MediaType LIKE 'Fixed hard disk%')
select SerialNumber from Win32_BaseBoard where SerialNumber <> NULL
select * from Win32_DiskDrive where not InterfaceType='USB'
SELECT __RELPATH, DiskIndex FROM Win32_DiskPartition WHERE (DiskIndex<>NULL) AND (DiskIndex=0)
